1
00:00:10,090 --> 00:00:14,010
Students and working adults
have completely different values.

2
00:00:14,010 --> 00:00:17,060
It's exhausting waiting for someone
to come home, too.

3
00:00:19,480 --> 00:00:23,770
Kamiki-san, I finished the documents.

4
00:00:24,570 --> 00:00:28,320
Are you talking about work
even in your sleep?

5
00:00:31,110 --> 00:00:36,450
Sigh, a little brother
who needs constant care.

6
00:00:52,340 --> 00:00:54,350
K-Kamiki-san.

7
00:00:55,060 --> 00:00:59,230
Talk about a rookie
who needs constant looking after.

8
00:00:59,980 --> 00:01:01,390
Huh?

9
00:01:01,810 --> 00:01:04,810
Clumsy rookies
are actually kind of cute.
